metadata.name: OBLIVION
metadata.description:
Oblivion is born from the clash of two worlds, Maze’s new project O Eremita presents the words on top of Francesco Valente’s transverse flute, while the visuals are provided by Random Freaks.
The result is a piece of visual and sonic poetry that will gain even more meaning as we reach the end of this Kali Yuga.

Airdrop with extra content will be sent to the collector:

Original Music (audio)
Instrumental (audio)
Spoken word (audio)
Behind the scenes (video)

 
All behind the scenes: http://y2u.be/vbi2H18QFXg
 
Edition 1/1
